data.description: Welcome Home to South Crestview! Conveniently located on John King Road South of I10 ensures a quick trip to local Military Bases, Schools, and all that the area offers. This 3 Bedroom 3 Full Bath offers a spacious living room and kitchen outfitted with Black & Stainless-Steel Appliances. The bedrooms are all spacious in size. The addition through the living room into the backyard offers plenty of extra storage and a wet room to clean off if needed. The spacious, completely fenced backyard offers plenty of room for toys or entertaining. A large 15 x 12 Storage Shed offers additional storage as well. This is where you can set your feet up at the end of the day and call it home!
